data.description: Discover worry-free living in this meticulously updated 3 Bedroom, two bath home where all the hard work has been completed for you. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with brand-new features, including a NEW ROOF, GUTTERS, AC, AIR HANDLER, WATER HEATER, REFRIDGERATOR and MICROWAVE. More upgrades include the DISHWASHER, WASHER, DRYER AND RO TOUCHLESS KITCHEN FAUCET which are all less than 3 years old and add a touch of modern convenience. This charming home features an open, split floor plan designed for seamless entertaining. Vaulted ceilings, plant shelves, and a breakfast bar create an inviting atmosphere, 2 car attached garage and a spacious 12x10 Storage building in the backyard. Additional highlights include an indoor laundry room, fully fenced yard which provides the perfect blend of comfort and outdoor enjoyment. Nestled in an established neighborhood conveniently close to I75 and Lamarue Elementary School This home is not in a flood zone and is not deed restricted, offering you the freedom to make it truly your own. Check out the 3D tour by clicking the Virtual Tour button.
